l knowledge ", "meta": null, "access_control": {"read": {"group_ids": [], "user_ids": []}, "write": {"group_ids": [], "user_ids": []}}, "created_at": 1761699806, "updated_at": 1761785385, "user": {"id": "9b013030-56f5-4c63-ba8e-5761787d0787", "name": "chelule maina", "email": "chelumaina@gmail.com", "role": "admin", "profile_image_url": "/user.png"}, "files": [{"id": "0f90739a-1945-45c4-ae8a-c12e51255059", "hash": "d4328d59f403112112292e60617330b0b18485906f669854b0b33a65df05abe3", "meta": {"name": "The_Constitution_of_Kenya_2010.pdf", "content_type": "application/pdf", "size": 1717074, "data": {}, "collection_name": "3cf9924e-76bf-4186-9b46-6252f49d3fda"}, "created_at": 1761785349, "updated_at": 1761785349}, {"id": "6a5b11d3-e905-4cfd-9ef0-ebb5c7e088f7", "hash": "e2688d4f30374c18ea0786c4ec5bd52179f47ce33a21fd668fe1d9fbc59a18ad", "meta": {"name": "Civil Procedure Rules.pdf", "content_type": "application/pdf", "size": 1937344, "data": {}, "collection_name": "3cf9924e-76bf-4186-9b46-6252f49d3fda"}, "created_at": 1761700786, "updated_at": 1761700786}], "type": "collection"}, "document": ["affirm) that I will bear true faith and allegiance to the people and the  \\nRepublic of Kenya; that I will faithfully and conscientiously discharge  \\nmy  duties  as  Speaker/Deputy  Speaker  of  the  Senate/National  \\nAssembly;  that  I  will  obey,  respect,  uphold,  preserve,  protect  and \\ndefend this Constitution of the Republic of Kenya; and that I will do  \\nright to all manner of persons in accordance with this Constitution of  \\nKenya and the laws and conventions of Parliament without fear or  \\nfavour, affection or ill will (So help me God).\\n171", "G.H., Advocate for the plaintiff (or defendant).\\nTo E.F., Advocate for the defendant (or plaintiff)\\n________________________\\nForm No. 3\\nParticulars\\n(O. 2, r. 10 (6))\\n(Title)\\nThe defendant (or plaintiff) in answer to the Request for Particulars dated the ...................... day\\nof ....................., 20 ................ gives particulars as follows -\\n1. Of paragraph ............................................................. - (specify particulars given)\\n2. Of paragraph ...........................................................- (specify particulars given)\\n3. Of paragraph............................................................ - (specify particulars given)\\netc ....................................................................................................................\\n125", "except any such land that is occupied by the State organ as  \\nlessee under a private lease;\\n(c) land transferred  to  the State by way of sale, reversion or  \\nsurrender;\\n(d) land in respect of which no individual or community ownership  \\ncan be established by any legal process;\\n(e) land in respect of which no heir can be identified by any legal  \\nprocess;\\n(f) all minerals and mineral oils as defined by law; \\n(g) government forests other than forests to which Article 63 (2)  \\n(d) (i) applies, government game reserves, water catchment  \\nareas, national parks, government animal sanctuaries, and  \\nspecially protected areas;\\n(h)  all  roads  and  thoroughfares   provided  for   by  an  Act  of \\nParliament;\\n(i) all rivers, lakes and other water bodies as defined by an Act  \\nof Parliament;\\n41"], "metadata": [{"producer": "LibreOffice 3.6", "start_index": 0, "source": "The_Constitution_of_Kenya_2010.pdf", "creator": "Writer", "hash": "d4328d59f403112112292e60617330b0b18485906f669854b0b33a65df05abe3", "creationdate": "2013-02-28T17:50:04+03:00", "name": "The_Constitution_of_Kenya_2010.pdf", "title": "Rev. 2010]", "created_by": "9b013030-56f5-4c63-ba8e-5761787d0787", "embedding_config": "{'engine': '', 'model': 'sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2'}", "page": 170, "total_pages": 193, "page_label": "171", "author": "Andare Jeffrey", "file_id": "0f90739a-1945-45c4-ae8a-c12e51255059"}, {"total_pages": 276, "creator": "Apache FOP Version 2.4",